{"tid":117541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今年第4單。15歲男生憂學業墮樓亡 母痛哭：我以後點算","createTime":"2017-02-12T10:02:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-13T06:58:30.000Z","uid":73064,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"efb9fd302bd86e15541ce879045f2b59b3ae9565","tid":117541,"uid":73064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T10:02:46.000Z","msg":"【14:00】死者年僅15歲，受學業問題困擾<br />\n<br />\n農曆年假後一周，今日發生第四宗學童尋死事件。今早9時57分，馬鞍山錦泰苑錦邦閣15歲姓譚男生，被發現由大廈高處墮下，重傷倒卧地下奄奄一息，救護員到場證實他當場死亡。<br />\n<br />\n警方正展開調查，初步相信死者因學業問題不開心，由大廈天台墮下，現場未有撿獲遺書，事後聯絡死者父母到場認屍，其母獲知兒子死訊後掩面痛哭，哽咽：「我以後點算？」聞者心酸。<br />\n<a href=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170212/280pix/1486869088_b41c.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170212%2F280pix%2F1486869088_b41c.jpg&d=AW73mzr4JVDAANnbo7Up2P9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=212bb48f\" target=\"_blank\">http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170212/280pix/1486869088_b41c.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n這是農曆年假後第四宗學童尋死事件，當中兩宗先後有兩名學童不幸身亡。馬鞍山一名16歲男生於上周日墮樓身亡；隨後青衣一名13歲女生上周一早上出門上學，竟走到大廈梯間跳下，送院不治；上周三，黃大仙下邨龍吉樓一名12歲姓周中一女生，疑受學業問題困擾企圖跳樓，獲衝鋒隊警員救回安全地方。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288人<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170212&amp;guid=56293863&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170212%26guid%3D56293863%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=AW73mzr4JVDAANnbo7Up2P9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=e990325d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170212%26guid%3D56293863%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=c0636707\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170212&amp;guid=56293863&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"4e546bbe8b529ffef1f5cbff6f625c18a2374616","tid":117541,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T10:03:42.000Z","msg":"替你高興&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;謝安琪"},{"pid":"067471125f656242ab9e4829129e65827ec7bec9","tid":117541,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T10:04:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>替你高興&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;謝安琪</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3058f161789b19f461d14a45e44c4c0375fd53a1","tid":117541,"uid":73064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T10:05:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n各位同學仔，個世界好大<br />\n唔好比讀書影響太多<br />\n香港只係好好好好好細既地方"},{"pid":"c87ea438fb34e7285ab49cc5c9c02819da7e693a","tid":117541,"uid":3682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T10:07:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n各位同學仔，個世界好大<br />\n唔好比讀書影響太多<br />\n香港只係好好好好好細既地方</blockquote><br />\n咪懶樂觀咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b1a9370ee283da2ccbd38ebd6c70bcde6b8f1b9","tid":117541,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T10:08:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/f