663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T02:03:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>連登巴打們。有冇諗過大家組團自殺？<br />\n橫掂大家都冇咩希望。可能一齊成班人幾十人自殺。會引起人關注</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n港豬/政府就算面對1千人集體自殺<br />\n第日咪又係如常番工<br />\n<br />\n鼓吹人自殺做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個真<br />\n港豬根本wfc 人地死人地事 佢有得返工繼續做隻豬就得"},{"pid":"2098b687b13ea5a0f12384e4d25050e8aa391915","tid":117541,"uid":11970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T02:06:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個想講個陣你唔想聽<br />\n到你想聽個陣已經唔想講</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ffdab8a11efb309213262441a700befdb4933a4","tid":117541,"uid":35701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T02:12:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f14ffaf134a813676faa765e350202b650f8ba40","tid":117541,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T02:15:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老老實實,香港教育制度垃圾之外<br />\n老豆老母教仔方式都極度垃圾<br />\n成日話自己個仔垃圾,冇用話咩想激勵佢<br />\n屌你人地建立緊自我印象呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申:我老豆老母都係,中五之前諗緊離家出去同死</span></span></blockquote><br />\n我老豆都係 而家無人理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我老母就由我地自己搵自己鐘意既興趣"},{"pid":"1e2562a515ef84814cfadd041313e0cc6af63a0f","tid":117541,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T02:17:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇巴打知道吳局長係味開埠以來，咁多任教育局局長入面在任期間出現最多學生自殺既一位?</blockquote><br />\n仲有羅范<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過個時係老師自殺多"},{"pid":"b8d600186223dba8193865572b2778115f45e35e","tid":117541,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T02:27:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>公道講句 個教育制度一直以黎都係咁柒 唔係話冇問題 而係多左學生跳樓真係唔係好關呢樣事 而且今時今日入大學係易左 多左好多比垃圾讀既課程<br />\n以前我地都有考tsa 學校都有操 點解而家先黎反<br />\n問題就係班家長on9 自己係出面報幾廿樣野要d細路學 唔想細路要花時間幫學校考tsa就賴政府<br />\n自己日日鬧個仔廢 兇佢入唔到大學死緊 出左事又屌政府 政府唔會冇錯 但最大責任一定係on9家長</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一直都有去補習社幫啲小學生補習<br />\n（全部黎自屋村學校 唔係有錢家庭屋企人學識唔高）<br />\n從來冇見過佢地話做功課要做到十一十二點<br />\n（佢地一日都八至九樣功課）<br />\n亦都有做過私補幫比較出名嘅小學學生補<br />\n都冇見過話佢地做功課要做到十一二點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多時新聞去訪問話小朋友有壓力<br />\n多功課冇時間玩個啲一睇屋企格局就知係中產<br />\n好多時都係家長逼出嚟<br />\n小朋友辛苦跟唔上咪唔好入名校囉<br />\n屯門有間自然學校入去讀一定會令小朋友開心<br />\n但班家長一定唔會俾囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又要拎名校個名去曬命驚比唔上人<br />\n又要賴而家個教育制度有問題<br />\n好多時都係家長投訴令學校要加功課加興趣班加測驗<br />\n<br />\n到小朋友真係出事嘅時候就話好傷心<br />\n真係好想問班家長有冇關心過自己細路（除咗成績以外）？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊個家長唔驚個仔小學成績差讀band 3群埋班mk度<br />\n邊個唔驚第時個仔讀唔成書第時搵唔到食<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有 當你係個中學生 讀左band 1比你掹車入邊精英班<br />\n你死讀爛讀好辛苦讀都係合格左右<br />\n其他個個七八十分 無形壓力都好大<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當你考試好多份卷好努力溫但都知炒粉<br />\n家長日穿煲 你都會驚 自身都會給予壓力<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當家長睇住入讀較好學校嘅條件愈黎愈難<br />\n惡性競爭 你又忍心咩都唔做本pea個仔咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好矛盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3a707daa4a6443627a8beef9fb1aa3e647fdb8c","tid":117541,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T02:34:35.000Z","msg":"如果依度有學生又覺得好大壓力既<br />\n隨時開post呻 咁多巴絲打一定會比意見你地<br />\n信我地 學校成績真係無你地想像中咁重要"},{"pid":"173b3a0e397c07aa2338a4817655e30ed9e3f8c6","tid":117541,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T02:37:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>&quot;我&quot;以後點算???</blockquote><br />\n養兒防老</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &quot;我&quot;</blockquote><br />\n咁都有得假設同批鬥</blockquote><br />\n一句就批會唔會太simple</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n死左個仔第一時間諗&quot;我&quot;以後點算，點解唔批鬥得，搵錢工具呀宜家？個仔感受邊個理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1315a1c63b281b2869195895850ac3e0ccd08fb8","tid":117541,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T02:37:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/66525Zo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F66525Zo.jpg&h=3dd70a62&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n加拿大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97b1d442e9c31c06c0a44143e5802d18cd963661","tid":117541,"uid":38461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T02:37:40.000Z","msg":"高登仔真係好多痴線毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76be825a04dd410bd9fe426bec1828390c158499","tid":117541,"uid":35701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T02:38:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d6b623d5cbb3e2da0630310119ea19cc9d9fc91","tid":117541,"uid":47222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T02:41:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>公道講句 個教育制度一直以黎都係咁柒 唔係話冇問題 而係多左學生跳樓真係唔係好關呢樣事 而且今時今日入大學係易左 多左好多比垃圾讀既課程<br />\n以前我地都有考tsa 學校